channel.title: Not necessarily for servers
channel.description:
Well, this thread isn't necessarily for help on an error with a server, it's with Hamachi..
First: After I tried uninstalling Hamachi, (newest version), I got an error that I didn't have the uninstallation log, so it didn't work.
Second: After I exited Hamachi a few days ago, I got on a couple days later, tried to put it up, and it said "Failed to load Hamachi Configuration, this application will now close"
I tried doing this: Start Menu->Run->%APPDATA% and renaming the file like I was told to by a friend, I try, and it still doesn't work, can anyone tell me how to fix this error?
